<i>noun</i>: 팔소매 [팔쏘매], 옷소매 [옫쏘매], 소매 [소매] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>팔소매 [팔쏘매]</dt><br>
<dd>sleeve</dd><br>
<dd>윗옷의 양 팔을 덮는 부분.</dd><br>
<dd>Either of the parts of an upper garment that cover the arms.</dd><br>
<dt>옷소매 [옫쏘매]</dt><br>
<dd>sleeve</dd><br>
<dd>윗옷의 양 팔을 덮는 부분.</dd><br>
<dd>The part of an upper garment, one on each side, which covers both arms.</dd><br>
<dt>소매 [소매]</dt><br>
<dd>sleeve</dd><br>
<dd>윗옷의 양 팔을 덮는 부분.</dd><br>
<dd>A part of the upper garment that covers the two arms.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>